## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **Beta Bionics iLet 2023** = first FDA fully autonomous bionic pancreas — 사용자 carb counting 입력 없음 (체중만 입력). Tandem Control-IQ + Medtronic 780G hybrid closed-loop 와 차별화. 양자-VQE 의 algorithm + insulin pharmacokinetic 통합 modeling fit.
2. **Medtronic 780G 2023** = first FDA advanced hybrid closed-loop with auto correction bolus. 670G (2016) → 770G (2020) → 780G (2023) lineage. SmartGuard + Meal Detection.
3. **Tandem Control-IQ 2019** = first FDA hybrid closed-loop algorithm (t:slim X2 pump). DIY Loop community 의 #WeAreNotWaiting 압박 후 FDA 승인 가속.
4. **Insulet Omnipod 5 2022** = first FDA tubeless closed-loop. patch pump form factor + SmartAdjust algorithm.
5. **Tidepool Loop 2023** = first FDA do-it-yourself-derived closed-loop algorithm. DIY → FDA legitimacy bridge — RileyLink + iPhone-based manage.
6. **Vertex VX-880 2024** = first patient T1DM insulin-independent (ViaCyte 후속). iPSC-derived β-cell allogeneic — immunosuppression 필요. cell therapy 가 disease-modifying T1DM cure pathway 등극.
7. **insulin icodec 2024 EMA Awiqli** = first weekly basal insulin (Novo). albumin-binding + acylation 으로 reservoir formation. 한국 식약처 + FDA pending.
8. **DIY closed-loop 2016+ (Loop + AndroidAPS + OpenAPS)** = pre-FDA pioneer — patient community 가 algorithm + RileyLink 자체 개발. 2023 Tidepool Loop FDA 승인 후 FDA 정책 변화.
9. **Endogenix MK-2640 2014 Phase 1 fail (Merck)** = first systematic smart insulin glucose-responsive. PEGylation + boronate ester. 임상 fail 후 next-gen Anderson lab + i-insulin research 활발. 양자-VQE 의 boronate-glucose binding affinity prediction = next candidate primary target.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, T1DM/T2DM 임상 의미 한정. closed-loop algorithm 자체는 quantum 직접 fit 적음 (algorithm + biomechanical), insulin/glucagon/smart insulin 분자가 fit.

